    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>冰霜</strong>是一款手绘独立游戏，集复古和创新特色于一体，讲述了女孩乌苏拉在魔法世界中冒险的故事。游戏宛如纸质童话故事书的风格以及女主人公可爱的外貌，和后者逐渐显露的真实人格形成鲜明对比，给玩家带来冲击的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346350/extras/6e4c684d28c8b886b31b4b56442f42c1.poster.avif?t=1757607141\" width=616 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346350/extras/6e4c684d28c8b886b31b4b56442f42c1.webm?t=1757607141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346350/extras/6e4c684d28c8b886b31b4b56442f42c1.mp4?t=1757607141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特点</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏在传统的炸弹人风格的基础上，增加了其他新型多变的元素，比如完善的升级系统以及装备库存系统；魔法NPC和密室；内嵌手绘风格迷你小游戏；动画效果及游戏原声。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346350/extras/5d0c1a6a1287ed0afd3d20d8c21351eb.poster.avif?t=1757607141\" width=616 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346350/extras/5d0c1a6a1287ed0afd3d20d8c21351eb.webm?t=1757607141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346350/extras/5d0c1a6a1287ed0afd3d20d8c21351eb.mp4?t=1757607141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>危机四伏的游戏世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中有五个魔法生物世界，每个世界中都有不同种类的怪物以及难以预测的boss。玩家从冰雪荒原出发，爬过险峻陡峭的山峰，穿过危机四伏的地下城，最后会达到神秘的禁林。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346350/extras/d038e07e058ccd84a6abe5a56be2ffee.poster.avif?t=1757607141\" width=616 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346350/extras/d038e07e058ccd84a6abe5a56be2ffee.webm?t=1757607141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346350/extras/d038e07e058ccd84a6abe5a56be2ffee.mp4?t=1757607141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏情节</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏故事探讨了以个人牺牲来换取“更伟大的利益”的对与错。玩家在游戏中的选择会影响最终的结局：乌苏拉最后究竟会失去自我，还是会做出正确的决定？到底什么才是“正确”的？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346350/extras/ec5f29fcad674087616d221871038a6c.poster.avif?t=1757607141\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346350/extras/ec5f29fcad674087616d221871038a6c.webm?t=1757607141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346350/extras/ec5f29fcad674087616d221871038a6c.mp4?t=1757607141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>美术风格</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏主打手绘纸质风格的画风和动画，皆由专业创意设计师和3D视觉特效设计师制作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346350/extras/f1a124390e0aa479c789adff3268eedd.poster.avif?t=1757607141\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346350/extras/f1a124390e0aa479c789adff3268eedd.webm?t=1757607141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346350/extras/f1a124390e0aa479c789adff3268eedd.mp4?t=1757607141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
